::Bazooka::

    "Right this way." Bazooka lead the way. "Commander Magmatron we have a 
visitor."
    "Understood. I am on my way." Magmatron replied. "Bring him to my 
conference room."

______________________________________________________________________
::Magmatron::

    "You will have to excuse me for a moment. I have a new recruit to attend 
to. I will have Bazooka operate the machine."
    He entered the Conference room. "Bazooka report to the lab, you know what 
must be done." Bazooka left. "Greetings. I am Magmatron. What is your name?"
